{"tid":1604464,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"希望大家發夢唔好再唱肥媽首濕鳩歌","createTime":"2019-09-30T03:27:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T04:57:03.000Z","uid":118538,"like":58,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"2428fd3e4bbb5f40ab31866c9dc9ec4775f4094c","tid":1604464,"uid":118538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T03:27:23.000Z","msg":"我明白大家好憎黑警，我都好撚嬲<br />\n但發夢並唔適合唱呢啲咁諷刺咁玩味嘅歌<br />\n雨傘革命時，就係衰唱歌，令到氣氛散漫<br />\n手足警戒不足，隨時被狗捉<br />\n所以我寧願大家叫口號"},{"pid":"eeb31915f473015aeecb2eeb41611d9d89f2698a","tid":1604464,"uid":118538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T03:37:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c84ac94c753c351b4e004cb324b4d796499411d8","tid":1604464,"uid":165510,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T03:41:59.000Z","msg":"呢個真係要推<br />\n除咗喺商場真係唔好喺夢境唱"},{"pid":"562e3a4a66c8b6ac672d7f35afc206025585419e","tid":1604464,"uid":114487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T03:42:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eYXN7uT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeYXN7uT.jpg&h=8ce194f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6CA0H3e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6CA0H3e.jpg&h=879be3a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qXwGsuV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqXwGsuV.jpg&h=eaf524a0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cd0db9a7ee9297f7554d98b7c4903a2883e032df","tid":1604464,"uid":55917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T03:42:45.000Z","msg":"呢首仲嚇撚死人<br />\n以為咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6425f20e5f8b1af07ed98eaf31983d29b6aa1f16","tid":1604464,"uid":99607,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"201